<a name="pollution"><hr width=40%>

<h2>Pollution</h2>

<ul type=square>

<li><b><a href="partner_news/apr96_earthtimes.html">Persistent organic pollutants an increasing danger to life:</a></b><br>
While high-profile chemical spills and fires attract media attention, less is known about the long-term damage caused by highly toxic chemicals.  But they are linked with altering sexual behaviour and weakening immune systems.<p>

<li><b><a href="partner_news/wk51_earthtimes_ozone.html
">Agreement reached on ozone-depleting chemicals</a></b><br>
A meeting of 110 countries in Vienna has agreed further measures - which follow up on the 1987 Montreal Protocol - to limit the production of harmful ozone-destroying chemicals across the world. <p>
