<DOCHDR>
http://mickey.acri.fr:80/French/Activites/Env/env.html 194.98.101.6 19970124213455 text/html 9197
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 21:36:44 GMT
Server: Apache/1.2b4
