	    The scope of the Experimental Demonstrator is to capture user
	    requirements in the field of Coastal Zone. The work is performed
	    within the framework of a contract awarded by the European
	    Commission in preparation for the design and implementation
	    of the Centre for Earth Observation
	    (<A HREF="http://ceo-www.jrc.it:80/">CEO</A>).
	<TR>
