  <body BACKGROUND="/gifs/fond.jpg">

      <P ALIGN=CENTER>
	<STRONG>
	  <BIG><BIG>
	      WWW Resources
	    </BIG></BIG>
	</STRONG>
      </P>

      We give here the WWW resources used by ACRI. 
      <P>
	Please don't forget to add to the interesting links any resource
	available through WWW.
	To do this use your internal Earth Watch hotlist.
	This list will be useful only if every one adds its own
	prefered pages.
      <P>

	Hot List (Not yet completed)
      <P>
      <P>
	<A HREF="ftp://ftp.acri.fr/pub">FTP Access</A>
      <P>

      <P>
	<A HREF="artie.html">the <B>DOGPILE</B> Search</A><BR>
multi-engine search made available by <A HREF="http://www.dogpile.com">DOGPILE</A>. Thanks to them
      <P>
      <P>
	<A HREF="useen.html">the <B>USE IT!</B> simple form</A> for another multi-engine search.
      <P>

      <P>
	<A HREF="useadven.html">the <B>USE IT!</B> complex form</A> for another multi-engine search.
      <P>

      <P>
	<A HREF="search.html">Search Engines</A> (our list of most used search engines)
      <P>

      <P>
	<A HREF="simple-search.html">Search Engines (Simple version)</A>(the same list but without any graphic and options: the simpliest options have been taken).
      <P>
	
