<DOCOLDNO>IA073-000473-B023-265</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://mickey.acri.fr:80/English/Products/register.html 194.98.101.6 19970124214149 text/html 5079
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 21:43:43 GMT
Server: Apache/1.2b4
