<DOCHDR>
http://mickey.acri.fr:80/English/Studies/Spatial/gnc.html 194.98.101.6 19970124214706 text/html 8678
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 21:48:53 GMT
