<BODY BACKGROUND="/gifs/fond.jpg">
<H1>IMAPIX</H1>

<h3><a href="/French/Produits/IMAPIX/imapix.html"> <img align=middle src="/gifs/FLAGFR.jpg" alt="french flag">Cliquez ici pour lire la version francaise</A></h3>
<img src="/gifs/bar_marbre_noir2.gif">

<H2>Cartography from remote-sensing images</H2>

<big>
<ul>
Land use planning with soil occupation cartography : layout of urban areas, <br>
road system.<br>
<i>Forestry </i>: studies and management of forest.<br>
<i>Agriculture </i>:  analysis and survey of parcels.<br>
<i>Developing countries</i> : management of ressources, desertification, <br>
deforestation.<br>
Cartography and burned areas.<br>
Oceanography : cartography of fishing areas.<br>
</ul>
</big>
<BR><BR>
<CENTER>
<IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE SRC="imapix.gif" ALT="IMAPIX Sample">

</CENTER>

<H1>THE SOFWARE PACKAGE IMAPIX</H1>

<big>
The different applications have been done with the software package <b>IMAPIX</b>, which runs with digital images from satellites, map digitization, video digitization.
IMAPIX is also used in oceanography, geology, climatology, land use planning, agriculture.

</big>

<H1>MAIN FEATURES</H1>
<big>
IMAPIX works on micro-computers PC with MS-DOS, and on the main work-stations (IBM, SUN, HP, BULL, DEC, CETIA) with UNIX, X-WINDOWS,OSF-MOTIF environment.
</big>

<P>

<H2>Management, display, interaction</h2>
<BIG>
<DL>
<DT><DD><img src = "/gifs/rec_rouge.gif">Multilayer images (8, 16 or 32 bits) and related objects management (spectral) bands, histograms, statistics, polygons, look-up tables)<p>

<DT><DD><img src = "/gifs/rec_rouge.gif">
Histograms and look-up tables computation

<P>

<DT><DD><img src = "/gifs/rec_rouge.gif">
Colour display, magnification, colour table editing by independent tuning of red, green and blue channels
<P>

<DT><DD><img src = "/gifs/rec_rouge.gif">
Instant display of the pixel value and coordinates with mouse clicking
<P>

<DT><DD><img src = "/gifs/rec_rouge.gif">
Colour tables management
<P>

<DT><DD><img src = "/gifs/rec_rouge.gif">
Instant interactive contrast enhancement (linear, isopopulation, gaussian)
<P>

<DT><DD><img src = "/gifs/rec_rouge.gif">
Interactive profile extraction and display (curves and value) of up three layers simultaneously
<P>

<DT><DD><img src = "/gifs/rec_rouge.gif">
Interactive inlay of text or graphics in image
<P>

<DT><DD><img src = "/gifs/rec_rouge.gif">
Colour or black and white print-outs
<P>
</DL>
</BIG>

<H2>Combination and filtering</H2>
<ul>
<big>
Coloured combination of multi-spectral layers<br>
Mathematical combinations (sun, product, ratio, logarithm, exponential, ...)<br>
Logical combinations<br>
Linear or non-linear smoothing and filtering<br>
Space variant contrast stretching<br>
Computation of structure functions (variograms)<br>
</big>
</ul>
