      <H1>Coastal Zone Data</H1>

      <FONT SIZE="+2">
	An important issue of this server should be to provide oceanographic data
	for user costal zone community.
      <P>
	Today, this experimental server, allows for demonstration to access various data:
      <DL>
	<!--
      <DL>
      <DT> <IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="/gifs/redball.gif">
      <A HREF="cz_buoy.html">
	Real-time measurement (updated each 12 hours) coming from drifting buoys </A>
      <P>
	-->
	<DT> <IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="/gifs/redball.gif">
	  <A HREF="watis/CEOWATiS.html">
	    An important data base from GKSS about Wadden Sea (WATiS Database)</A>
      <P>

	<DT> <IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="/gifs/redball.gif">
	  <A HREF="http://me-www.jrc.it/dms/dms.html">
	    An ISPRA service which allows to activate a distant software 
	    about DMS model</A>
	</DL>
	</DL>

	  This service is still at prototype level. So, don't hesitate to give
	  us your <A HREF="cz_interests.html">feedback</A> about this
	  service and the available data.
	</FONT>

