&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[<a href="http://www.dogpile.com/tech.html"><font size = "-1">Technical
Notes</font></a>]
</p>
</center>

<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH="100%" >
<TR VALIGN=TOP>
<TD Width="30%"> Try <b>Arfie! and find what you are looking for.</b>.  Or try our
<a href="http://www.dogpile.com/index-a.html">new advanced search</a>.
</TD>
